不好给你答复，目前不方便说」。 9 日晚，澎湃新闻致电涉事医生齐某，对方表示不接受采访，称「相关部门已经调查了，具体听官方的公布消息」，后挂断了电话。宿迁一患者因脑梗去世，医生承认此前未成功植入脑血管支架并隐瞒 _ 直击现场 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b01610b1e4cdeb16136e0ee9a845282_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "139 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/605823854"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I04iG4Yru/adKEAMaCDk2OTA3NTY3IJO9j6QGMAA4lQFAA3IIOTY5MDc1Njd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1686391661.575392", "card_id": "Q_602124752", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "刻在人类基因中里的禁令有哪些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8fba58602a86da7978f302e428ab6fc2_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "134 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602124752"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I04iG4Yru/adKEAMaCDk2MDg2MDA2IM2xo6MGMAA4jQJABHIIOTYwODYwMDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1686391661.575961", "card_id": "Q_343791192", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 669}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "二十万的轿车跟四十万的轿车究竟差别在哪里？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e1a649c6259d1245d75243f5ed1dac13_720w.jpg"}, "m